'''Geoff Hampson''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Awards===

* [[Fishbein Trophy]] (1) 2005
* [[Herman Trophy]] (1) 2003
* [[Mott-Smith Trophy]] (1) 2003

===Wins===

* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (1) 2001 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>

* [[Rosenblum Cup]] (1) 2010 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-open-teams.aspx Rosenblum Cup Winners]</ref>

* [[Buffett Cup]] (2) 2006, 2010 

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (1) 2008 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

